text: Big City is a 1937 American drama movie directed by Frank Borzage and starring Luise Rainer, Spencer Tracy, Irving Bacon, Oscar O'Shea, Victor Varconi, Eddie Quillan, Janet Beecher. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer. ==Other websites== * * Category:1937 drama movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Frank Borzage
